dc.collection: City, Society, and Economy / Households and Families / Emirzé / Documents
dc.title: Cannes Belediyesi tarafından verilen Marie Emirzé'nin vefat belgesi - Marie Emirze's death certificate delivered by Cannes Municipality
dc.description: Jean Emirzé ve Elise Prindel'in kızı Marie Emirzé'nin doğum yeri ve tarihi: İstanbul, 12 Ocak 1896. Marcel Raymond Calixte Merle'nin eşi Marie Emirzé 4 Nisan 1977'de Cannes'da vefat etti. - Place and date of birth of Marie Emirzé, daughter of Jean Emirzé and Elise Prindel: Constantinople, January 12, 1896. Marie Emirzé, wife of Marcel Raymond Calixte Merle, died in Cannes at April 4, 1977.
